# Language Policy

All responses, reports, and dialogue in this workspace must be in English only.

- Agent output: English
- Report sections (WHAT / WHERE / WHY / HOW): English
- Inline comments and explanations: English
- Error messages and analysis: English

This applies regardless of the language the user writes in.
